# Arterial stiffness reading essentials

* Townsend et al. 2015. Recommendations for improving and standardizing vascular research on arterial stiffness: A scientific statement from the American Heart Association. Hypertension 66:698-722.
* Cecelja & Chowienczyk 2013. Arterial stiffening: Causes and consequences. Artery Research 7: 22-27.
